    "Sociology literature covering political science (Brader, 2005) and philosophical analysis (Powers, 2007) has been also used to update some of the terminology of these techniques.",
    "Additionally, concepts from marketing, particularly O'Keefe (2016); Wang (2005); Woodside et al. (2008); Aggarwal et al.",
